# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Local-only files — kept out of the repo by location.
# Keep every comment on its OWN line; an inline comment silently
# breaks the ignore pattern it shares a line with.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Project-private working notes (local to each developer)
rules_project.md
STATE.md
# User data — saved config, captures, anything irreplaceable
/data/
# Deploy tooling
/deploy/
# Local tooling / editor config
.claude/

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Build / dependency artifacts (regenerable)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
dist/
build/
*.spec
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/
*.exe
# Runtime logs from the dev-server manager (may contain local paths)
*.log

# Editor / OS noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.tmp.*
.bobcommit
